<item chapterid="588715" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1918" articlename="办公室情缘" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1520598055" lastupdate="1520598055" chaptername="第761章" chapterorder="752" size="3210" saleprice="8" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    几天之后，我和几个客户经理正在外边跑市场，突然接到了霹雳丫的电话。

