<item chapterid="588770" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1918" articlename="办公室情缘" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1520598055" lastupdate="1520598055" chaptername="第816章" chapterorder="807" size="3134" saleprice="8" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    霹雳丫现在很是无助，内心很是纠结，她现在已经把我的话都奉若神明了，几乎我说的每句话，她都能听到心坎里去。

