<item chapterid="588942" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1918" articlename="办公室情缘" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1520598055" lastupdate="1520598055" chaptername="第988章" chapterorder="979" size="3202" saleprice="8" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    又争执了几个来回，花小芬看我主意已定，只好说：好吧，那我先回去，等这边的造船工程一结束，我立即带人过来到岛上去设计布置。

